      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ZIPPING KORDA (8) is a progressive type who recorded her 7th career win last time out (23.90) at this track. Hard to go past form here at this journey. Has a strong record from box 8, including two wins. Will go close again if runs up to latest. ANOTHER MEGHAN (2) has a strong record this track and trip with six wins and four placings from 18 starts. Placed last time (23.81) at this track in a Grade 3/4, finishing third and beaten 1.5 lengths. Looks suited here and can measure up. CAMBLA BLISS (1) returned a better run last time, finishing in the money (23.62) at this track behind Roxy Cambla in a Grade 4. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Some good form is emerging from her last run. Can measure up. CLEAR BLUE SKY (3) cannot be written off despite a miss here at his latest outing.",
